title: How Swift developers handle errors
excerpt: Mixed-method study investigation the error handling patterns of Swift developers.
citation: N. Cassee, G. Pinto, F. Castor and A. Serebrenik, "How Swift Developers Handle Errors," 2018 IEEE/ACM 15th International Conference on Mining Software Repositories (MSR), Gothenburg, 2018, pp. 292-302.
